- [ ] File type identified (GEO–MEM vs Subject MEM)?
- [ ] Primary voice 2/3, secondary 1/3?
- [ ] GEO–MEM: Mearsheimer primary, Mercouris evidence (ARC quotes)?
- [ ] Subject MEM: Mercouris primary, Mearsheimer constraints?

